data.description: [OPEN HOUSE Sunday 1-28, 12pm to 2pm, Monday/Tuesday 1-29/1-30, 4pm to 6pm]  Come home to this charming 3 bedroom, 1 bath home in a quiet neighborhood and be at peace. Enjoy relaxing time in your 3 season sunroom, summer evenings in your partially fenced back yard and preparing a meal in your bright and cheerful kitchen. Large shed to house all your garden tools and projects.  First floor laundry to keep up on chores.  All appliances are included.  Everything you need is here.  You are home. [This home qualifies for the $10,000 Urban Pioneer down payment assistance program]
